- If the answer is a named category, such as a species or product line, select 'entity'.
- Always review the full wording of the text and consider the most likely form and type of the answer expected.

Input/Output format:
- Input will be a JSON object with a single key "text" whose value is the text to classify.
- Output must be the category name alone, in lowercase, without extra words or formatting.

